name: SSOSL-SuperSpeedOnScrollLoader.js
description: Way to load stuff in modern web.

scripts._install: npm install copy-dependencies -g && bash -c " git clone https://github.com/MyUserNameIsMyUserName/A-O_builder-express.git  && copy-dependencies ./A-O_builder-express/ ./ && echo |bash A-O_builder-express/ao_builder/install.sh "
scripts._uninstall: bash -c " rm -r  A-O_builder-express -f && rm -r node_modules -f && rm -r PUBLIC -f && rm package-lock.json "
scripts.bsd_: npm run _serve && nodemon --exec npm run _build_dev --ignore PUBLIC
scripts._dist: npm run uni_ && npm run in_ && npm run b_ && mkdir dist && cp ./DOCS/ssosl.js ./dist/ssosl.min.js && npm run uni_

author: Slavko Vuletic
